Information about the house

Single-family home located just blocks from KU and downtown Lawrence!

Three bedrooms, two baths, living room, family room, dining room and heated garage.

Fenced backyard. Perfect for a gregarious dog!

Entertainment center alcove in family room, wood floors, fire place, shady backyard.

Home comes with newer appliances, including dishwasher and garbage disposal.

Walk to KU, two parks, city swimming pool, library and the great downtown.

Quiet neighborhood of owner-occupied homes and discreet rental properties. Enjoy the walkable charm of Old West Lawrence.
